CRM & Lead Source Integrations

Connect your primary systems of record. These connections power lead ingestion, enrichment, and CRM updates.

Salesforce
Demo connection for enterprise CRM lead sync.
Not connected

Jazon reads:

• Lead and contact fields (name, email, company, title)

• Account data (industry, size, region)

• Activity history (emails, calls, meetings)

Jazon writes:

• Qualification status and ICP score

• Next best action and AI recommendations

• Logged activities for outreach and follow-up

HubSpot
Demo connection for marketing and lifecycle leads.
Not connected

Jazon reads:

• Lifecycle stage and lead source

• Campaign and email engagement history

• Form submissions and key properties

Jazon writes:

• Qualification outcome and reason

• Primary outreach channel and status

• Notes for SDR and AE follow-up tasks
